Regular League Match

Rogue

Lifetime record (3-2)

BRIX
Grimlock
HT: 5'5
WT: 122lbs
Lifetime record (0-0)
Not Ranked
Amber is 3-0 this season, undefeated and ranked 9th. As last year's lightweight Champion, Amber wants another title and hopes to up her ranking to improve her position in the Summer Vengeance Tournament.
Brix is a newcomer with 6 months of Jiu-Jitsu that she took a few years back. The last person that came to us with that kind of experience was the Ninja. But, to be fair, the Ninja had years of training.
This is a little war; both go full-out for the entire time. Both girls give more then they have. However, the Rookie comes away with the upset and gets to fuck the veteran in the ass hard and deep.
title: Amber Rayne "Rogue" (3-2)
